{"tid":2336393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這些法官只是站在專制暴行的一方　奪剝你我他香港人的民主","createTime":"2020-12-22T14:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T16:35:38.000Z","uid":261647,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"663f91f82945254f20dea7d9b6005dccf0b4e016","tid":2336393,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:25:43.000Z","msg":"https://twitter. com/LungZenoOpen/status/1341338719979098113<br />\n<br />\n香港人作為人類，被剝奪了民主，要復還民主。復還到的民主權利是反對和阻礙的人都有份的。講權利，是阻止人阻礙復還所有人權利。就算他不想要，但我們要，他不應剝奪大家權利。現在是專制，且一小部份人當上政府，以暴行維持專制。禁蒙面法是讓專制者和其奴僕肆虐。這些法官站在專制暴行方，絕不平衡。"},{"pid":"55f4ff0aa6344afe9f4f0494fec7a05457c96d4b","tid":2336393,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"睇標題仲以為係啲咩改歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f78bca88cd64e1fbd8ce1d31f0132f6ad61f32f","tid":2336393,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"法官只是站在專制暴政的一方<br />\n奪剝香港人的民主<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faf2164c0688d9896875a84ce6d9a9b6c00b0c9","tid":2336393,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55f4ff0aa6344afe9f4f0494fec7a05457c96d4b","tid":2336393,"uid":150100,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"睇標題仲以為係啲咩改歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"寫唔寫到成首歌詞出黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}